ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gyhxhaj</a>"},{"pid":"afd916ec1877817ee458899a3ace820344c5a72a","tid":1792583,"uid":173160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"你推幾重"},{"pid":"972a0772a0d0328f34254f4ff3b969e6316eee5f","tid":1792583,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e801fdd89870187edf4403236d873e01cf944616","tid":1792583,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"首先要消炎止痛先<br />\n跟住唔可以一黎就做番以前推既動作<br />\n要注重番旋轉慢慢練番肌肉既彈性 <br />\n跟住先好操番以前既LEVEL <br />\n<br />\nmore details :<br />\nNASM certified personal trainer <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gyhxhaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgyhxhaj&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3MbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9c823aca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gyhxhaj</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"...係咪都叫人消炎止痛先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 護士"},{"pid":"ee0c220e6ec635856ead527605f731ff6e4c965a","tid":1792583,"uid":141237,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係專業，<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好睇小人既身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好可能係你搏頭既肌肉腫起左，拎到你做動作既時候，d唔應該卡到既空位因為腫起左所以卡住令到你痛同有聲。<br />\n<br />\n依家最重要或者咁講響無專業指導下，你可以做既有，了解返你日常既動作同習慣有無導致以上情況。<br />\n<br />\n例如用電腦用得多，搏頭會前傾，都有可能導致你推胸各樣動作用錯位置發力，例如推胸因為搏頭前傾變左用前搏發力，令到搏頭壓力山大，導致局部腫脹。<br />\n<br />\n所以依家最好睇返自己平時有d咩壞習慣導致你身體邊度「咩」左或者邊度前傾咁，再上網睇返d動作點做再重新發力去做，正常如果d錯既位用返啱既力去做，你身體唔洗睇醫生就會自然恢復返。<br />\n<br />\nps，當然前提要拉筋，不過我覺得唔係個個都咁有熱誠同恆心，都係量力而為啦"},{"pid":"9925fd586a8cbe2301e97a0806fd058a10d7fa1c","tid":1792583,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"放棄果d動作"},{"pid":"fa4e78c3436378ce2844bfbeab7d983585bfdef3","tid":1792583,"uid":78819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"用熱水浸下？多啲血到好得快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6b372e0a82ff5ba0a4ddf75a6fe2e3b4d50b1d","tid":1792583,"uid":254813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"大把呢d熱身唔做，又唔夠力又要威show off，放啞鈴大大聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6ad4ff6937ad935c59cfb5e6d3c83d64376ca3","tid":1792583,"uid":280183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"睇左鐵打未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42daf90226f47b6b4ed677917295c1e8ddbfc5dc","tid":1792583,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"我左膊舊骨都試過用深蹲時整傷<br />\n依家用力㩒落去都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb68a8dcc8dafaa372c0f0fe335f686499187b75","tid":1792583,"uid":191107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"轉行出街靛野啦"},{"pid":"c04b20390bd2bf6fa5ac6f91a7b7acfcc85f4fd3","tid":1792583,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972a0772a0d0328f34254f4ff3b969e6316eee5f","tid":1792583,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e801fdd89870187edf4403236d873e01cf944616","tid":1792583,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"首先要消炎止痛先<br />\n跟住唔可以一黎就做番以前推既動作<br />\n要注重番旋轉慢慢練番肌肉既彈性 <br />\n跟住先好操番以前既LEVEL <br />\n<br />\nmore details :<br />\nNASM certified personal trainer <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gyhxhaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2